sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Watch as Smartwatch
    participant App as Watch-App
    participant Server as Backend Server

    User->>Watch: Open Watch-App
    Watch->>App: Request data
    App->>Server: Fetch user data
    Server-->>App: Return user data
    App-->>Watch: Send data to display
    Watch-->>User: Show data on screen
    User->>Watch: Interact with app
    Watch->>App: Send user interaction
    App->>Server: Update user data
    Server-->>App: Confirm update
    App-->>Watch: Notify update success
    Watch-->>User: Show update success message